Module org.apache.jena.querybuilder

Package org.apache.jena.arq.querybuilder.clauses

package org.apache.jena.arq.querybuilder.clauses
Interfaces that describe various SPARQL clauses as per http://www.w3.org/TR/2013/REC-sparql11-query-20130321. These classes are used to compose consistent interfaces for specific builder implementations.
